# 📂 04 — Review & Handoff

**Business function:** Background Art Production — 2D Animation Studio  
**Trigger:** P08 asset documentation completed and supervisor approval fields signed off  
**Prompts in this section:** P09, P10

---

## Section Purpose

The review and handoff section forms the final gate of the background production pipeline — conducting a structured quality checklist review across all previous pipeline outputs before formally handing the background off to the receiving department.  
These two prompts ensure that no background leaves the department with unresolved pipeline issues, undocumented continuity dependencies, or missing sign-offs.  
Together they create a formal, auditable handoff record that protects both the background department and receiving departments from downstream errors.

## Chain Diagram
```
P08 asset documentation completed and approved
      ↓
[P09 RUNS — conducts final quality checklist review]
      ↓
PASS / CONDITIONAL PASS resolved → continues
FAIL → returned to relevant pipeline stage for correction
      ↓
[P10 RUNS — generates formal handoff brief]
      ↓
Both departments sign off
      ↓
Background file transferred to receiving department
```

